@node BRASS "Brass-Talon Chimera"

@{b}Brass-Talon Chimera@{ub}

Color   = Colorless
Rarity  = VI(U)
Type    = Artifact Creature (2/2)
Cost    = 4
Artist  = Mike Dringenberg
 
Text(VI): First strike.
          Brass-Talon Chimera counts as a Chimera.
          Sacrifice Brass-Talon Chimera: Put a +2/+2 counter on target
          Chimera and that Chimera gains first strike permanently.

Flavor Text: @{i}No Flavor Text

 @{b}NO RULINGS@{ub}

@endnode
@node DIAMO "Diamond Caleidoscope"

@{b}Diamond Caleidoscope@{ub}

Color   = Colorless
Rarity  = VI(R)
Type    = Artifact
Cost    = 4
Artist  = Ron Spencer 

Text(VI): <3T>: Put a Prism token into play. Treat this token as a 0/1
          artifact creature.
          Sacrifice a Prism token: Add one mana of any color to your
          mana pool. Play this ability as a mana source.

Flavor Text: @{i}``A pretty toy. Now show me its tactical applications.''
               -Telim'Tor

 @{b}NO RULINGS@{ub}

@endnode
