@node IRONH "Iron-Heart Chimera"

@{b}Iron-Heart Chimera@{ub}

Color   = Colorless
Rarity  = VI(U)
Type    = Artifact Creature (2/2)
Cost    = 4
Artist  = Mike Dringenberg

Text(VI): Attacking does not cause Iron-Heart Chimera to tap.
          Iron-Heart Chimera counts as a Chimera.
          Sacrifice Iron-Heart Chimera: Put a +2/+2 counter on target
          Chimera and attacking any turn does not cause that Chimera
          to tap.

Flavor Text: @{i}No Flavor Text

 @{b}NO RULINGS@{ub}

