@node SANDS "Sands of Time"

@{b}Sands of Time@{ub}

Color   = Colorless
Rarity  = VI(R)
Type    = Artifact
Cost    = 4
Artist  = Paul Lee

Text(VI): Each player skips his or her untap phase. At the beginning of each
          player's turn, untap each tapped artifact, creature, and land he or
          she controls and tap each untapped artifact, creature, and land he
          or she controls.

Flavor Text: @{i}``But once, with a magician's help, Time was stopped and
               Day stood still.'' -``Love Song of Night and Day''

 @{" Rulings " link MTG_CARD_S.guide/SAOFT}

@endnode
